lead_paragraph: Leticia Romero hit back-to-back 3-pointers and Emiah Bingley added a third as No. 19 Florida State opened with an 11-0 run in a 75-42 rout of Boston College in the Seminoles' Atlantic Coast Conference home opener Thursday night.

headline.print_headline: No. 19 Florida State Women Rout Boston College, 75-42
